Azure offers a variety of migration tools:

* Azure Migrate
* Azure Data Box
* Azure Database Migration Service
* AzCopy

For example, Azure Migrate handles VM migrations, while Data Box is used for large-scale offline transfers.

A real-life use case is migrating enterprise workloads from on-premise to Azure.

Another example is transferring petabytes of data using physical devices.

These tools provide flexibility for different migration needs.
